comments.body:
Could substantially reduce the size of the json output (by about 20%) by changing this to:

```json
{
  "new_table": {
    "0/2": {
      "address": "89.78.111.197:8333",
      "services": 1037,
      "source": "34.126.67.135"
    },
    "0/5": {
      "address": "13.228.211.83:8333",
      "services": 1033,
      "source": "34.126.67.135"
    }
}
```

